data.description: Looking for space?? Don't miss out on this beautiful 4/2.5 with 2343 sqft. As you walk in notice no carpet, an open floor plan and a bonus area. The kitchen provides a sizable pantry, granite counter tops, island and stainless appliances. The living room is adorned with a decorative fireplace and natural light passing through the windows. There is also a 1/2 bath and drop zone by the 2 car garage. Step upstairs to find 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths (one of which is the primary bedroom's en suite) and the laundry room. The primary bedroom provides a spacious walk in closet and the ensuite boasts dual vanities, separate shower and soaking tub. When you walk out to the large back patio, escape the sun under the gazebo and enjoy the view of your fenced in back yard, lush trees and greenery. Some extras this home offers are a water purification system, storage shelving in the garage, wireless camera doorbell and auto garage door opener. The neighborhood amenities include a pool, playground, walking trail, clubhouse and fitness center.
